	<pb facs="liv_002043_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><placeName><settlement type="town">Hamilton</settlement></placeName> <add place="above" rend="gray" hand="#U">25</add> <date when="1865-08-08">8 August <add place="above" rend="gray" hand="#U">62</add>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="words"/>18<add place="inline">[64]</add></date></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Noel</persName></p>
<lb/><p>The kind true
<lb/>heartedness of your
<lb/>father and mother
<lb/>at <unclear cert="medium"><placeName>Warley House</placeName></unclear>
<lb/>I can never forget
<lb/>and I thank you 
<lb/>for your very
<lb/>kind invitation
<lb/>and evident
<lb/>desire to follow

	<pb facs="liv_002043_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>in your dear parents
<lb/>"spoor" but I am
<lb/>very anxious to get
<lb/>back to <placeName><bloc>Africa</bloc></placeName> again
<lb/>and endeavour to
<lb/>open up the country
<lb/>North of the <term type="people"><term type="nationality">Portuguese</term></term>
<lb/>so that my past
<lb/>labours may not
<lb/>be rendered fruitless
<lb/>by these inveterate
<lb/><term type="occupation"><orgName>slavers</orgName></term> - I left my
<lb/>steamer at <placeName><settlement type="city">Bombay</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>for this very purpose
<lb/>and am now only
<lb/>anxious to get into
<lb/>a retired nook to do

	<pb facs="liv_002043_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>a little work and then <add place="above" hand="#U" rend="gray">63</add>
<lb/>be off. <choice><sic>my</sic><corr>My</corr></choice> daughter
<lb/>now woman grown
<lb/>is to keep my cottage
<lb/>as I wish to be near
<lb/>her as much as
<lb/>possible - I avoid
<lb/>all public engagements
<lb/>except <placeName><settlement type="town">Bath</settlement></placeName> - I
<lb/>mention these
<lb/>things that you
<lb/>may see that I do 
<lb/>not undervalue
<lb/>your generous
<lb/>hospitality though
<lb/>I have to decline it

	<pb facs="liv_002043_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>I beg you to present
<lb/>my kind salutation 
<lb/>to your husband &amp;
<lb/>accept my warmest
<lb/>thanks for your
<lb/>kind offer</p>

